const dekHtml = "Dashboard distrust is one of the most common and most misdiagnosed problems in business intelligence. Organizations fix the wrong thing — the visualization, the tool, the data freshness — and the trust problem persists. That's because trust fails for reasons that have almost nothing to do with data accuracy.";
